I ran further than I planned... 10k in 53 minutes.

Took it really steady to get round, but didn't expect to keep going for this distance. I saw a black tame rabbit (it didn't scarper immediately when it saw me) and less chavvy litter (not so much McDonalds or Kentucky buckets).
